snippet: The jet crashed on a residential street in a Southern California desert community Wednesday evening, setting two homes on fire, but there was no immediate word of any injuries.
abstract: Military jet crashes on residential street in Imperial, Calif, setting two homes on fire; pilot ejects safely and there is no immediate word of any injuries.
lead_paragraph: The jet crashed on a residential street in a Southern California desert community Wednesday evening, setting two homes on fire, but there was no immediate word of any injuries.

headline.main: California: Military Pilot Ejects as Jet Crashes Into Houses
